OL,5, Rishi Sunak has been accused of failing
OL,6, to act soon enough to save #11bn of    
OL,7, taxpayers' money that has been used to 
OL,8, pay interest on government debt.       
OL,10,FThe National Institute of Economic and 
OL,11,FSocial Research (NIESR) said the losses
OL,12,Fstemmed from the chancellor's failure  
OL,13,Fto insure against interest rate rises. 
OL,15,FIt meant higher than necessary payments
OL,16,Fon #900bn of reserves created through  
OL,17,Fthe quantitative easing (QE) programme.
OL,19,FThe Treasury said it has "a clear      
OL,20,Ffinancing strategy" on debt.           
